		--><div style="height:9.396cm;width:14.666cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">مُحِبَّةً لِصَفْوَةِ أَوْلِيَائِكَ مَحْبُوبَةً فِي أَرْضِكَ وَ سَمَائِكَ </span></p><p class="P21"><span class="T14"><br/></span><span class="T14">lass sie die Liebe zu Deinen Reinen und aufrichtigen Freunden empfinden,</span><span class="T14"><br/></span><span class="T14">lass sie beliebt und respektiert auf der Erde und in den Himmeln sein,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:10.098cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page10" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.401cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P25"><span class="T24"> </span><span class="T18">صَابِرَةً عَلَى نُزُولِ بَلاَئِكَ‏ شَاكِرَةً لِفَوَاضِلِ نَعْمَائِكَ </span></p><p class="P21"><span class="T14"><br/></span><span class="T14">lass sie ruhig und gelassen sein inmitten von Unglücken,</span><span class="T14"><br/></span><span class="T14">lass sie dankbar sein in Wohlstand,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page11" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.228cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P25"><span class="T18">ذَاكِرَةً لِسَوَابِغِ آلاَئِكَ مُشْتَاقَةً إِلَى فَرْحَةِ لِقَائِكَ </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">lass sie leidenschaftlich sein,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">in der Sehnsucht nach dem herzerwärmenden Treffen mit Dir;</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page12" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.999cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">مُتَزَوِّدَةً التَّقْوَى لِيَوْمِ جَزَائِكَ‏ مُسْتَنَّةً بِسُنَنِ أَوْلِيَائِكَ</span><span class="T14"> </span></p><p class="P21"><span class="T14"/></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16">gut ausgestattet mit Frömmigkeit,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">um mein Ende zu erlangen an dem Tag der Belohnung,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page13" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:7.923cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">مُفَارِقَةً لِأَخْلاَقِ أَعْدَائِكَ</span></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">مَشْغُولَةً عَنِ الدُّنْيَا بِحَمْدِكَ وَ ثَنَائِكَ</span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16">lass sie distanziert sein von der Angewohnheit Deiner Feinde, lass sie ihre Zeit in dieser Welt damit verbringen, Dich zu lobpreisen und Dich zu verherrlichen.</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page14" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.122cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">اللَّهُمَّ إِنَّ قُلُوبَ الْمُخْبِتِينَ إِلَيْكَ وَالِهَةٌ</span><span class="T14"> </span><span class="T10">وَ سُبُلَ الرَّاغِبِينَ إِلَيْكَ شَارِعَةٌ</span><span class="T25"> </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">Oh Allah, wahrlich, die Herzen derer,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">die sich Dir hingeben, sind erfüllt von leidenschaftlicher Liebe, </span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page15" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.43cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ أَعْلاَمَ الْقَاصِدِينَ إِلَيْكَ وَاضِحَةٌ </span></p><p class="P27"><span class="T10">وَ أَفْئِدَةَ الْعَارِفِينَ مِنْكَ فَازِعَةٌ</span><span class="T10"> </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">und die Anzeichen derer,die den Weg zu Dir nehmen, sind deutlich. Die Herzen der Wissenden fürchten Dich,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page16" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:7.72cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ أَصْوَاتَ الدَّاعِينَ إِلَيْكَ صَاعِدَةٌ </span></p><p class="P27"><span class="T10">وَ أَبْوَابَ الْإِجَابَةِ لَهُمْ مُفَتَّحَةٌ</span><span class="T10"> </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">und die Stimmen der Rufenden steigen zu Dir empor, und die Türen der Anerkennung sind für sie geöffnet.</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page17" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:7.72cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ دَعْوَةَ مَنْ نَاجَاكَ مُسْتَجَابَةٌ </span></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ تَوْبَةَ مَنْ أَنَابَ إِلَيْكَ مَقْبُولَةٌ </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">Jeder der sein Flehen Dir vorbringt,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">erhält eine gefällige Antwort,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">jeder der reumütig umkehrt zu Dir, erhält </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16">Deine Annahme,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.137cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page18" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.003cm;width:15.124cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P22"><span class="T15">وَ عَبْرَةَ مَنْ بَكَى مِنْ خَوْفِكَ مَرْحُومَةٌ وَ الْإِغَاثَةَ لِمَنِ اسْتَغَاثَ بِكَ مَوْجُودَةٌ </span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20">jeder der aus Angst vor Deiner Bestrafung in Tränen ausbricht,</span><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20">erhält Erbarmen (Barmherzigkeit),</span><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20">jeder der Abhilfe für etwas sucht, </span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page19" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.426cm;width:15.001cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ الْإِعَانَةَ لِمَنِ اسْتَعَانَ بِكَ مَبْذُولَةٌ</span></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ عِدَاتِكَ لِعِبَادِكَ مُنْجَزَةٌ</span><span class="T25"> </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">so findet er die erforderliche Unterstützung bei Dir, um sie zu beseitigen, jeder der um Deine Hilfe bittet, erhält Hilfe von Dir als Geschenk. </span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.499000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page20" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.599cm;width:15.067cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P22"><span class="T15">وَ زَلَلَ مَنِ اسْتَقَالَكَ مُقَالَةٌ</span><span class="T26"> </span></p><p class="P22"><span class="T27">وَ أَعْمَالَ الْعَامِلِينَ لَدَيْكَ مَحْفُوظَةٌ </span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T28"><br/></span><span class="T28"><br/></span><span class="T28"> </span><span class="T28">der um Vergebung für seine Fehler bittet,</span><span class="T28"><br/></span><span class="T28">findet diese vor als wären sie nicht gewesen, jeder der alles um Seinetwillen unternimmt, wird erfahren das alles und jede Tat (Handlung) bewahrt bleibt.</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.499000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page21" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.828cm;width:15.265cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P20"><span class="T13"/></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ أَرْزَاقَكَ إِلَى الْخَلاَئِقِ مِنْ لَدُنْكَ نَازِلَةٌ </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">Die Möglichkeiten des Unterhalts (Versorgung),</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">bereitgestellt für Deine Geschöpfe, kommen von Dir wie ein Regenfall.</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.499000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page22" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.228cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ عَوَائِدَ الْمَزِيدِ إِلَيْهِمْ وَاصِلَةٌ </span></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ ذُنُوبَ الْمُسْتَغْفِرِينَ مَغْفُورَةٌ</span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T20">Und es erreichen sie als Beigabe viele wiederkehrende Gefälligkeiten und Gaben, in regelmäßigen Abständen, die Sünden von jenen welche um Vergebung bitten, sind übersehen,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page23" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.198cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P22"><span class="T15">وَ حَوَائِجَ خَلْقِكَ عِنْدَكَ مَقْضِيَّةٌ </span></p><p class="P22"><span class="T15">وَ جَوَائِزَ السَّائِلِينَ عِنْدَكَ مُوَفَّرَةٌ </span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20">die Bedürfnisse von all dem welches von Dir erschaffen wurde, sind in rechter Art und Weise zufriedengestellt, jene, welche eine aufrichtige Bitte vorbringen, diese sind es die noch mehr erhalten als nach dem sie fragten,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page24" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.599cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ عَوَائِدَ الْمَزِيدِ مُتَوَاتِرَةٌ </span></p><p class="P18"><span class="T10">وَ مَوَائِدَ الْمُسْتَطْعِمِينَ مُعَدَّةٌ</span><span class="T25"> </span></p><p class="P23"><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">einer nach dem anderen,</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">wieder und wieder erneut;</span><span class="T16"><br/></span><span class="T16">für die Hungrigen erfordertes Essen bereitgestellt,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page25" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:8.43cm;width:15.063cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P18"><span class="T10">و</span><span class="T15"> مَنَاهِلَ الظِّمَاءِ مُتْرَعَةٌ </span></p><p class="P24"><span class="T15">اللَّهُمَّ فَاسْتَجِبْ دُعَائِي وَ اقْبَلْ ثَنَائِي</span><span class="T26"> </span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T20">für die Durstigen reines Wasser in Fülle.</span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T20">Oh Allah, gebe mir eine wohltuende Antwort auf mein Bitten und erkenne meine Lobpreisung an welche ich in Verehrung aufsage,</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:13.364cm;width:16.799cm; padding:0; " class="P17"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""/></div></div></div><div style="clear:both; line-height:0; width:0; height:0; margin:0; padding:0;"> </div><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:page'.--><div id="page26" class="dp3"><!--Next '
			div' is a draw:frame.
		--><div style="height:9.599cm;width:15.164cm; padding:0; " id="Rectangle_3" class="P11"><!--Next 'div' was a 'draw:text-box'.--><div style=""><p class="P22"><span class="T15">وَ اجْمَعْ بَيْنِي وَ بَيْنَ أَوْلِيَائِي‏</span></p><p class="P22"><span class="T15">بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَ عَلِيٍّ وَ فَاطِمَةَ وَ الْحَسَنِ وَ الْحُسَيْنِ </span></p><p class="P28"><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20"><br/></span><span class="T20">lass Frieden, Ruhe und Einklang zwischen mir und meinen Freunden sein, dem Propheten, Ali, Fatima, Hassan und Hussein zuliebe;</span></p></div></div><!--Next 'div' added for floating.--><div style="position:relative; left:9.701000000000001cm;"><!--Next '
